descriptionHtml:
This is my ENB preset, now lets get this out hte way before you ask, performance wise i dont know what itll be like for you but for me i lose about 10 to 20 fps sooooo yea but here some options for gaining performance back
-Turn off DOF (Depth of Field)
-Turn off Subsurface Scattering
-Turn off Sun Rays
-Experiment! Turn everything off and back on or whatever anywho back to explaining wait....theres nothing to explain..Enjoy The Preset!!! (btw adding your own screenshots will help lots!!


Specs
Windows 10 64bit
DDR3 16gb RAM
AMD Radeon 200 Series (2gb DDR5 VRAM)
AMD FX 870K Quad Core CPU (3.60GHz)
author: Lillbearzski
